jibe.sdk.client.videosharing
Class VideoSharingEvent

java.lang.Object
  jibe.sdk.client.events.JibeEvent
      jibe.sdk.client.events.JibeSessionEvent
          jibe.sdk.client.videosharing.VideoSharingEvent

public class VideoSharingEvent
extends JibeSessionEvent

Event class, containing the event codes specific to video-sharing sessions. These are not created by the client app, but should be listened for, and processed.

Note that the video-session ID that this event refers to is obtained by inspecting the inherited method JibeEvent.getInfo().

Constructor Detail

VideoSharingEvent

public VideoSharingEvent(int eventCode,
                         long source,
                         long info)
Creates a new video-sharing event. A client application will not create this object, but will simply inspect the object returned by the SDK.

Parameters:
eventCode - The event code.
source - The source of the event - the video-sharing session ID.
info - Additional information, such as error codes.
